what should be done with him.

783
01:22:17,643 --> 01:22:20,237
What should be done with him?

784
01:22:25,218 --> 01:22:27,015
I don't know.

785
01:22:27,520 --> 01:22:29,511
I don't think that's true.

786
01:22:29,722 --> 01:22:32,316
I think you have some
very definite ideas...

787
01:22:32,525 --> 01:22:34,220
...about what should be done
with Danny.

788
01:22:34,427 --> 01:22:37,021
And I'd like to know
what they are.

789
01:22:38,931 --> 01:22:40,728
Well, I...

790
01:22:41,033 --> 01:22:45,436
...I think maybe he should be taken
to a doctor.

791
01:22:45,638 --> 01:22:48,937
You think "maybe"
he should be taken to a doctor?

792
01:22:51,177 --> 01:22:54,510
When do you think "maybe"
he should be taken to a doctor?

793
01:22:55,147 --> 01:22:56,512
As soon as possible?

794
01:22:57,116 --> 01:22:59,448
"As soon as possible?"

795
01:23:02,121 --> 01:23:03,554
Please.

796
01:23:04,957 --> 01:23:08,222
You believe his health
might be at stake.

797
01:23:09,795 --> 01:23:11,319
Yes.

798
01:23:12,665 --> 01:23:15,293
And you are concerned about him.

799
01:23:17,870 --> 01:23:20,100
And are you concerned about me?

800
01:23:20,940 --> 01:23:22,100
Of course I am.

801
01:23:22,308 --> 01:23:24,538
Of course you are!

802
01:23:24,744 --> 01:23:27,872
Have you ever thought about
my responsibilities?

803
01:23:28,080 --> 01:23:29,570
What are you talking about?

804
01:23:29,782 --> 01:23:32,615
Have you ever had
a single moment's...

805
01:23:32,818 --> 01:23:34,877
...thought about
my responsibilities?

806
01:23:35,087 --> 01:23:37,351
Have you ever thought
for a single moment...

807
01:23:37,556 --> 01:23:40,354
...about my responsibilities
to my employers?!

808
01:23:40,626 --> 01:23:42,457
Has is ever occurred to you...

809
01:23:42,662 --> 01:23:46,154
...that I have agreed to look after
the hotel until May 1st?

810
01:23:46,399 --> 01:23:48,424
Does it matter to you at all...

811
01:23:48,634 --> 01:23:51,728
...that the owners have placed
their complete confidence in me...

812
01:23:51,937 --> 01:23:55,065
...and that I have signed
a letter of agreement...

813
01:23:55,274 --> 01:23:57,868
...in which I've accepted
that responsibility?

814
01:23:58,344 --> 01:24:00,369
Do you have the slightest idea...

815
01:24:00,579 --> 01:24:03,810
...what a moral and ethical
principal is? Do you?!

816
01:24:04,183 --> 01:24:07,277
Has it ever occurred to you what
would happen to my future...

817
01:24:07,486 --> 01:24:09,886
...if I fail to live up to
my responsibilities?

818
01:24:10,089 --> 01:24:12,387
Has it ever occurred to you?
Has it?!

819
01:24:12,591 --> 01:24:14,115
Stay away from me!

820
01:24:14,994 --> 01:24:16,052
Why?

821
01:24:16,362 --> 01:24:19,331
I just want to go back to my room.

822
01:24:19,532 --> 01:24:20,794
Why?

823
01:24:21,434 --> 01:24:22,298
Well...

824
01:24:23,436 --> 01:24:25,461
...I'm very confused.

825
01:24:26,605 --> 01:24:30,268
And I just need a chance
to think things over.

826
01:24:31,310 --> 01:24:35,246
You've had your whole fucking life
to think things over!

827
01:24:35,448 --> 01:24:38,212
What good's a few minutes more
going to do you now?

828
01:24:39,185 --> 01:24:40,675
Stay away from me!

829
01:24:41,020 --> 01:24:42,317
Please!

830
01:24:43,089 --> 01:24:44,147
Don't hurt me.

831
01:24:44,357 --> 01:24:45,688
I'm not going to hurt you.

832
01:24:45,891 --> 01:24:47,085
Stay away from me!

833
01:24:47,293 --> 01:24:48,157
Stay away!

834
01:24:48,361 --> 01:24:49,350
Darling.

835
01:24:49,562 --> 01:24:51,120
Light of my life.

836
01:24:51,564 --> 01:24:52,895
I'm not going to hurt you.

837
01:24:53,099 --> 01:24:55,090
You didn't let me finish
my sentence.

838
01:24:55,301 --> 01:24:57,496
I said,
"I'm not going to hurt you."

839
01:24:57,703 --> 01:25:00,467
I'm just going to bash
your brains in.

840
01:25:00,740 --> 01:25:03,709
I'm going to bash them
right the fuck in.

841
01:25:04,777 --> 01:25:06,335
Stay away from me!

842
01:25:06,846 --> 01:25:07,870
Stay away from me!

843
01:25:08,080 --> 01:25:10,480
I'm not going to hurt you.

844
01:25:10,750 --> 01:25:12,274
Stay away from me!

845
01:25:12,518 --> 01:25:13,576
Stay away!

846
01:25:14,453 --> 01:25:15,681
Please!

847
01:25:16,722 --> 01:25:18,485
Stop swinging the bat.

848
01:25:18,691 --> 01:25:19,953
Stay away from me.

849
01:25:20,726 --> 01:25:22,023
Put that bat down, Wendy.

850
01:25:22,228 --> 01:25:23,718
Stop it!

851
01:25:25,197 --> 01:25:26,323
Give me the bat.

852
01:25:26,532 --> 01:25:27,658
Please!

853
01:25:27,900 --> 01:25:30,095
- Stay away!
- Give me the bat.

854
01:25:30,302 --> 01:25:31,360
Stop it!

855
01:25:31,604 --> 01:25:33,037
Give me the bat.

856
01:25:33,372 --> 01:25:34,999
- Stay away from me.
- Stop swinging the bat.

857
01:25:35,207 --> 01:25:36,572
Please stop!

858
01:25:36,776 --> 01:25:37,970
Give me the bat.

859
01:25:38,177 --> 01:25:39,405
Stay away from me.

860
01:25:39,678 --> 01:25:42,044
- Stop it!
- Give me the bat.

861
01:25:43,449 --> 01:25:44,473
Goddamn...!

862
01:26:59,758 --> 01:27:01,453
What are you doing?

863
01:27:04,263 --> 01:27:05,730
Wait a minute.

864
01:27:07,132 --> 01:27:09,123
What are you doing?

865
01:27:11,971 --> 01:27:13,199
What are you doing?

866
01:27:27,086 --> 01:27:28,576
Wait a minute!

867
01:27:30,956 --> 01:27:32,548
What are you doing?

868
01:27:32,791 --> 01:27:34,520
Open the door!

869
01:27:35,828 --> 01:27:36,852
Goddamn it!

870
01:27:37,062 --> 01:27:40,623
Let me out of here!
Open the goddamn door!

871
01:27:44,336 --> 01:27:45,564
Wendy, listen.

872
01:27:46,005 --> 01:27:48,940
Let me out and I'll forget
the whole goddamn thing.

873
01:27:49,141 --> 01:27:51,609
It'll be just like
nothing ever happened.

874
01:28:06,292 --> 01:28:07,657
Baby.

875
01:28:08,861 --> 01:28:12,160
I think you hurt my head
real bad.

876
01:28:13,766 --> 01:28:15,427
I'm dizzy.

877
01:28:16,435 --> 01:28:18,630
I need a doctor.

878
01:28:25,511 --> 01:28:26,705
Honey.

879
01:28:29,381 --> 01:28:31,713
Don't leave me in here.

880
01:28:40,326 --> 01:28:42,226
I'm going to go now.

881
01:28:45,297 --> 01:28:47,128
I'm going to try...

882
01:28:47,333 --> 01:28:50,325
...to get Danny down
the Sidewinder...

883
01:28:51,036 --> 01:28:53,402
...in the Snowcat today.

884
01:28:55,641 --> 01:28:57,472
I'll bring back a doctor.

885
01:29:02,848 --> 01:29:04,713
I'm going to go now.

886
01:29:12,157 --> 01:29:15,957
You've got a big surprise
coming to you.

887
01:29:17,429 --> 01:29:20,023
You're not going anywhere.

888
01:29:21,700 --> 01:29:25,830
Go check out the Snowcat and the
radio, and you'll see what I mean.

889
01:29:30,442 --> 01:29:32,137
Go check it out.

890
01:29:34,279 --> 01:29:36,474
Go check it out!

891
01:29:39,852 --> 01:29:41,786
Go check it out.

892
01:31:29,628 --> 01:31:32,028
It's Grady, Mr. Torrance.

893
01:31:32,765 --> 01:31:34,733
Delbert Grady.

894
01:31:36,301 --> 01:31:37,893
Grady?

895
01:31:58,357 --> 01:32:00,188
Hello, Grady.

896
01:32:04,863 --> 01:32:06,660
Mr. Torrance...

897
01:32:08,600 --> 01:32:12,331
...I see you can hardly
have taken care of the...

898
01:32:13,071 --> 01:32:15,562
...business we discussed.

899
01:32:22,281 --> 01:32:25,216
No need to rub it in, Mr. Grady.

900
01:32:26,084 --> 01:32:30,145
I'll deal with that situation
as soon as I get out of here.

901
01:32:31,023 --> 01:32:33,753
Will you indeed, Mr. Torrance?

902
01:32:34,259 --> 01:32:36,090
I wonder.

903
01:32:37,262 --> 01:32:39,355
I have my doubts.

904
01:32:40,566 --> 01:32:44,798
I, and others, have come
to believe...

905
01:32:45,003 --> 01:32:47,995
...that your heart is not in this.

906
01:32:48,640 --> 01:32:51,165
That you haven't the belly for it.

907
01:32:57,349 --> 01:33:01,649
Just give me one more chance
to prove it, Mr. Grady.

908
01:33:02,487 --> 01:33:04,421
That's all I ask.

909
01:33:05,958 --> 01:33:10,224
Your wife appears to be stronger
than we imagined, Mr. Torrance.

910
01:33:10,429 --> 01:33:11,896
Somewhat more...

911
01:33:12,097 --> 01:33:14,065
...resourceful.

912
01:33:14,333 --> 01:33:17,097
She seems to have got
the better of you.

913
01:33:20,339 --> 01:33:23,001
For the moment, Mr. Grady.

914
01:33:23,742 --> 01:33:25,903
Only for the moment.

915
01:33:27,813 --> 01:33:31,977
I fear you will have to deal
with this matter...

916
01:33:32,251 --> 01:33:35,914
...in the harshest possible way,
Mr. Torrance.

917
01:33:36,488 --> 01:33:38,046
I fear...

918
01:33:38,323 --> 01:33:40,883
...that is the only thing to do.

919
01:33:44,363 --> 01:33:46,456
There's nothing
I look forward to...

920
01:33:46,665 --> 01:33:50,567
...with greater pleasure,
Mr. Grady.

921
01:33:51,970 --> 01:33:54,700
You give your word on that,
do you, Mr. Torrance?

922
01:33:56,174 --> 01:33:58,199
I give you my word.

923
01:35:10,315 --> 01:35:12,875
Redrum.

924
01:35:13,819 --> 01:35:16,379
Redrum.

925
01:37:24,349 --> 01:37:25,907
Danny, stop it!

926
01:38:22,707 --> 01:38:24,174
I'm home.

927
01:39:01,513 --> 01:39:04,380
Come out, come out,
wherever you are.

928
01:39:29,941 --> 01:39:31,806
I can't get out.

929
01:39:32,611 --> 01:39:33,737
Run!

930
01:39:34,579 --> 01:39:36,012
Run and hide!

931
01:39:36,548 --> 01:39:37,674
Run!

932
01:39:37,882 --> 01:39:39,110
Quick!

933
01:39:40,819 --> 01:39:45,347
Little pigs, little pigs,
let me come in.

934
01:39:51,096 --> 01:39:54,497
Not by the hair
on your chinny-chin-chin?

935
01:39:56,034 --> 01:39:58,093
Then I'll huff...

936
01:39:58,303 --> 01:40:00,203
...and I'll puff...

937
01:40:00,405 --> 01:40:02,464
...and I'll blow your house in!

938
01:40:17,389 --> 01:40:18,754
Please!

939
01:40:19,491 --> 01:40:21,254
Don't!

940
01:40:21,926 --> 01:40:23,450
Don't!

941
01:40:42,047 --> 01:40:43,275
Stop it!

942
01:40:47,519 --> 01:40:49,077
Here's Johnny!

943
01:43:31,149 --> 01:43:32,377
Hello?

944
01:43:37,822 --> 01:43:39,585
Anybody here?

945
01:44:01,679 --> 01:44:03,237
Hello?

946
01:44:15,560 --> 01:44:17,391
Anybody here?

947
01:44:47,358 --> 01:44:49,292
Anybody here?

948
01:45:30,301 --> 01:45:31,996
Danny-boy!

949
01:48:12,830 --> 01:48:14,764
I'm coming!

950
01:48:17,268 --> 01:48:19,202
I'm coming, Dan!

951
01:49:19,997 --> 01:49:22,397
Great party, isn't it?

952
01:49:40,051 --> 01:49:42,281
I'm coming!!

953
01:49:44,856 --> 01:49:47,154
You can't get away!

954
01:49:51,028 --> 01:49:53,428
I'm right behind you!

955
01:53:18,469 --> 01:53:20,494
- Mommy!
- Danny, come here!

956
01:53:21,705 --> 01:53:23,434
Mommy.

